data.description:
VA assumable Loan at 2.25%! 
Beautiful home in Cobblestone Creek golf course neighborhood w/ fresh paint throughout & brand new carpet! Upon entry you'll find a large living space w/ soaring ceilings & beautiful wood Floors brining then living space & formal dining space together. The Kitchen boasts ample Cabinets : Granite Counters : Stainless Appliances : Pantry : Breakfast Eating Space w/ bay window overlooking backyard. The primary Bedroom is situated privately downstairs that also contains a bay window making the Room a great size. En Suite located off the Bedroom w/ double vanity : separate soaking tub & shower : walk-in Closet. Upstairs you'll find 2 very generously sized bedrooms (so rare to find!) w/ great Closets & a Loft Space that would work great as a Playroom/Office/additional Living Space. In the backyard you'll find a covered patio space w/ no Homes directly behind you for additional privacy. This Home sits directly across from the Par 3 Golf Course (included in HOA fees) & neighborhood also includes a great clubhouse & Pool. Move in Ready for you today!
